---
title: Mushroom Ravioli and Creamy Goat Cheese Sauce with Snap Peas and Walnut Crumb
description: This dish brings together some of the season's best flavours: mushroom, goat cheese and walnuts. A little hint of white wine in a cream sauce adds a touch of luxury!
